snippet.title: Minecraft: Sonic Texture Pack - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
See the world through the eyes of Sonic, your favorite blue hedgehog! This complete texture pack, inspired by iconic zones like Green Hill and Labyrinth, transforms your entire world into a unique but familiar landscape! Just beware the hostile mobs — they've gotten a Badnik new look!

Sprint to the Marketplace today: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=63e0e2fc-749f-4bbe-b047-223df2755f39

To report issues or get help please go to our support site: https://support.gamemodeone.com/hc/en-us
